{"tid":357212,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)人‧神‧魔戰1-2","createTime":"2017-08-12T16:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T19:10:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56950c15c079f7a2bf79e6ef9b9d338a289ed7a9","tid":357212,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Pn%2Bceepx2f6L6EIMe%2FR%2FSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fa98ae7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Pn%2Bceepx2f6L6EIMe%2FR%2FSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6ca7e3e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有dailymotion<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Pn%2Bceepx2f6L6EIMe%2FR%2FSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=019cf87e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/80/Clashofthetitansremakeposter1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F80%2FClashofthetitansremakeposter1.jpg&h=4e03b429&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fe/Wrath_of_the_Titans.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffe%2FWrath_of_the_Titans.jpg&h=4504e1d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.權力鬥爭促使人民與統治者，及統治者與神之間的對立；但眾神之間的戰爭卻會摧毀整個世界。在人間成長的珀爾修斯（山姆&middot;沃辛頓飾）要從復仇心重的冥王黑帝斯（雷夫&middot;范恩斯飾）手中拯救自己的家人。珀爾修斯憑著無懼勇氣，自薦向冥王宣戰以換取天帝宙斯（連恩&middot;尼遜飾）的神力並解放人間地獄。帕修斯於是帶領著士兵朝著詭異的世界展開冒險之旅..<br />\n<br />\n2.擊敗海怪多年後，半人神柏修斯拒絕了宙斯邀請他前往神界治理天下的請求，而是選擇留在凡間當漁夫，並與過世妻子伊俄所生的10歲兒子西里斯過著平凡生活。一天晚上，宙斯下凡探訪柏修斯。因人民不再祈禱，眾神的力量逐漸消失殆盡，且囚禁克羅諾斯地下闇牢將會崩毀，所以宙斯需要同柏修斯合作，以對抗即將到來的威脅。不過，柏修斯因顧慮家人的安全而拒絕參與..<br />\n<br />\n12 40AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Pn%2Bceepx2f6L6EIMe%2FR%2FSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1f49e376\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Pn%2Bceepx2f6L6EIMe%2FR%2FSPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a97099cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f750e29bac832952f9e5d52f1c5945dfa854f6d5","tid":357212,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3916e4ac5a2cd77dc64ef78f1a1084e2055e8c9","tid":357212,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif